-It's not too late
for me to kill you.

37:22.710 --> 37:25.895
-Where am I going?

37:25.900 --> 37:28.698
You said I would be safe.

37:28.710 --> 37:29.768
We spent the night together.

37:29.770 --> 37:32.580
We don't know even
know each other's name.

37:32.590 --> 37:35.297
But your name isn't
your name, is it?

37:35.300 --> 37:38.053
Is your face your face?

37:38.060 --> 37:39.755
Are your children your children?

37:56.380 --> 37:57.085
-Oh, wait.

37:57.090 --> 37:57.897
Why?

37:57.900 --> 37:58.594
Why?

37:58.600 --> 38:00.875
No, you can't do this!

38:00.880 --> 38:02.871
Where are you taking me?

38:02.880 --> 38:04.142
Help me!

38:04.150 --> 38:04.832
-Quiet.

38:09.490 --> 38:10.969
You'll be home for
Passover after all.

38:16.850 --> 38:17.828
-No.

38:17.830 --> 38:19.582
Etai!

38:19.590 --> 38:20.284
Etai!

38:20.290 --> 38:22.508
You promised!

38:22.520 --> 38:23.976
You promised me!

38:36.400 --> 38:37.128
