I have a right to know.

38:42.950 --> 38:44.895
-I'm not going to kill you.

38:49.800 --> 38:53.133
-You want me to work for you?

38:53.140 --> 38:54.084
-Not for me.

38:54.090 --> 38:55.580
-No, of course.

38:55.590 --> 38:58.605
You-- you're just
obeying orders.

38:58.610 --> 38:59.304
Like Eichmann.

39:02.860 --> 39:05.806
