away from my family?

39:19.600 --> 39:20.419
-You're adaptable.

39:20.420 --> 39:22.308
You've proven that much.

39:28.030 --> 39:30.248
-Let me work for you from here.

39:30.250 --> 39:32.059
Eh?

39:32.060 --> 39:34.574
I have my lab, my resources.

39:34.580 --> 39:35.842
I'll give you things
your government

39:35.850 --> 39:37.488
