ECM, you know what that means?

39:40.200 --> 39:42.145
Electronic Counter Measures.

39:42.150 --> 39:44.892
Radar, infrared, lasers--
they can all be deceived.

39:44.900 --> 39:48.347
I can give this to you.

39:48.350 --> 39:49.726
I'll put you on the ARPANET.

39:49.730 --> 39:52.278
This you don't have
in the Soviet Union.

39:52.280 --> 39:52.974
Please.

39:56.990 --> 39:58.958
Don't send me back there.

