44:40.260 --> 44:40.954
-Agent Beeman.

44:53.690 --> 44:56.534
You must know who I am as well.

44:56.540 --> 44:58.474
Oleg Igorevich Burov.

44:58.480 --> 45:01.324
I noticed you on my
tail an hour ago.

45:01.330 --> 45:05.073
Did you think I would lead
you somewhere interesting?

45:05.080 --> 45:06.126
Where are your colleagues?

45:06.130 --> 45:07.210
