45:07.220 --> 45:08.938
-Where is Anton Baklanov?

45:08.940 --> 45:10.760
-Who?

45:10.770 --> 45:13.159
Are you going to shoot me?

45:13.160 --> 45:15.276
I am a diplomat, a
guest in your country.

45:19.090 --> 45:19.852
-Turn around.

45:19.860 --> 45:21.157
-I'm here to talk
about Nina Sergeevna.

45:24.120 --> 45:25.849
This is a unique
opportunity for us.

45:34.330 --> 45:35.774
Here we are.

45:38.690 --> 45:41.488
Put the gun away.

45:41.500 --> 45:45.539
Nina is in such great risk.

45:45.540 --> 45:46.996
-What are you talking about?

45:47.000 --> 45:48.729
-Please.

45:48.740 --> 45:51.834
No one else knows that
you're running her.

45:51.840 --> 45:53.751
Not yet.

45:53.760 --> 45:56.376
I'm the only one.

45:56.380 --> 45:58.792
That's what matters.

45:58.800 --> 46:03.339
No, I didn't tell anybody at the
Rezidentura what I figured out.

46:03.340 --> 46:08.323
I'm a-- a budding
student of capitalism.

46:08.330 --> 46:11.276
Everything has a value.

46:11.280 --> 46:15.569
Everything can be traded, yes?

46:15.580 --> 46:19.755
So, let's make a deal.

46:19.760 --> 46:25.312
What can you give me in
exchange for Nina's safety?

46:33.570 --> 46:34.548
